(3, 'lecture', 'lecture', '演讲,讲课 (n&v.)', 'n&v.', '/''lektʃə/', '{"meaning":"演讲,讲课 (n&v.)","examples":["...a series of lectures by Professor Eric Robinson. — …埃里克·鲁滨逊教授的系列讲座。","lecture on — 有关…的演讲；训斥；告诫","lecture note — 讲义，上课笔记"],"etymology":null}', 505),
