(3, 'description', 'description', '描写,形容;种类 (n.)', 'n.', '/dɪ''skrɪpʃ(ə)n/', '{"meaning":"描写,形容;种类 (n.)","examples":["The booklet gives a brief description of each place. — 这本小册子对每一个地方都作了简短的介绍。","Berlin sounds fascinating from your description. — 从你的描述来看，柏林是个迷人的城市。","detailed description — 详细描述；详细说明"],"etymology":null}', 985),
(3, 'prescription', 'prescription', '药方,处方 (n.)', 'n.', '/prɪ''skrɪpʃ(ə)n/', '{"meaning":"药方,处方 (n.)","examples":["We are trying to cut the price of prescription drugs . — 我们正努力降低处方药的价格。","a repeat prescription — 重复处方","folk prescription — 偏方；民间药方"],"etymology":null}', 986),
