(3, 'subscribe', 'subscribe', '(to)订阅，订购；同意vt.捐助，赞助 (v.)', 'v.', '/səb''skraɪb/', '{"meaning":"(to)订阅，订购；同意vt.捐助，赞助 (v.)","examples":["I''ve personally never subscribed to the view that either sex is superior to the other. — 我个人从未持有过一种性别比另一种性别优越的观点。"],"etymology":null}', 988),
