(3, 'secondary', 'secondary', '次要的,二级的;中级的,第二的 (adj.)', 'adj.', '/''sek(ə)nd(ə)rɪ/', '{"meaning":"次要的,二级的;中级的,第二的 (adj.)","examples":["the novel’s secondary characters — 这本小说中的次要人物","secondary school — 中等学校","secondary market — 二级市场；次级市场"],"etymology":null}', 994),
(3, 'consequence', 'consequence', '结果,后果,影响;重要性 (n.)', 'n.', '/''kɒnsɪkw(ə)ns/', '{"meaning":"结果,后果,影响;重要性 (n.)","examples":["I don’t suppose it is of any consequence now. — 现在我觉得这事一点都无所谓了。","as a consequence — 因此，结果","in consequence — 因此；结果"],"etymology":null}', 995),
(3, 'consequently', 'consequently', '结果，因此，所以 (adv.)', 'adv.', '/''kɒnsɪkw(ə)ntlɪ/', '{"meaning":"结果，因此，所以 (adv.)","examples":["Most computer users have never received any formal keyboard training. Consequently, their keyboard skills are inefficient. — 大多数的电脑使用者都没有经过正规的键盘操作训练，因此他们的键盘技巧不够熟练。","The molecules are absorbed into the bloodstream and consequently affect the organs. — 这些分子被吸收到血液里，从而影响到器官。"],"etymology":null}', 996),
(3, 'sequence', 'sequence', '先后,次序;连续,数列 (n.)', 'n.', '/''siːkw(ə)ns/', '{"meaning":"先后,次序;连续,数列 (n.)","examples":["Be careful to perform the actions in the correct sequence . — 注意要按正确的顺序来完成动作。","in sequence — 依次，逐一","time sequence — 时间顺序"],"etymology":null}', 997),
(3, 'subsequent', 'subsequent', '随后的,后来的 (adj.)', 'adj.', '/''sʌbsɪkw(ə)nt/', '{"meaning":"随后的,后来的 (adj.)","examples":["These skills were passed on to subsequent generations. — 这些技能代代相传。","subsequent pages of the book — 接下去的书页","subsequent events — 财务报表编制后发生的事项"],"etymology":null}', 998),
(3, 'sense', 'sense', '感官;感觉;判断力;意义 (n.)；觉得,意识到 (v.)', 'n.', '/sens/', '{"meaning":"感官;感觉;判断力;意义 (n.)；觉得,意识到 (v.)","examples":["Cats have a very acute sense of hearing (= very good, so that they can hear even the smallest sound ) . — 猫的听觉非常敏锐。","sense of — …的感觉","in a sense — 在某种意义上"],"etymology":null}', 999),
(3, 'absence', 'absence', '缺乏，不存在；缺席，不在；缺席的时间 (n.)', 'n.', '/''æbs(ə)ns/', '{"meaning":"缺乏，不存在；缺席，不在；缺席的时间 (n.)","examples":["In the absence of any evidence, the police had to let Myers go. — 警察没有证据，只好把迈尔斯放了。","absence of — 缺乏","in the absence of — 缺乏，不存在；无…时，缺少…时"],"etymology":null}', 1000);
