(3, 'absent', 'absent', '缺席的；缺乏的,不存在的;心不在焉的 (adj.)', 'adj.', '/''æbs(ə)nt/', '{"meaning":"缺席的；缺乏的,不存在的;心不在焉的 (adj.)","examples":["The dull, absent look on her face implied boredom. — 她脸上呆滞、茫然的神情说明她觉得无聊了。","absent from — 缺席","absent minded — 健忘的"],"etymology":null}', 1001),
(3, 'consensus', 'consensus', '(意见等的)一致，一致同意，共识 (n.)', 'n.', '/kən''sensəs/', '{"meaning":"(意见等的)一致，一致同意，共识 (n.)","examples":["The EU Council of Finance Ministers failed to reach a consensus on the pace of integration. — 欧盟财政部长会议未能就一体化的进度达成共识。","the current consensus of opinion — 目前观点上的一致","The general consensus was that technology was a good thing. — 大家都认为科技是好东西。"],"etymology":null}', 1002),
(3, 'consent', 'consent', '(to)同意,赞成,答应 (v&n.)', 'v&n.', '/kən''sent/', '{"meaning":"(to)同意,赞成,答应 (v&n.)","examples":["The chairman was elected by common consent (= with most people agreeing ) . — 主席是大家一致推选出来的。","divorce by mutual consent — 双方均同意的离婚","informed consent — 知情同意，知会同意；知后同意"],"etymology":null}', 1003),
(3, 'essence', 'essence', '本质,实质 (n.)', 'n.', '/''es(ə)ns/', '{"meaning":"本质,实质 (n.)","examples":["In essence his message was very simple. — 实质上他想表达的意思很简单。","in essence — 本质上；其实；大体上","of the essence — 非常重要的"],"etymology":null}', 1004),
(3, 'essential', 'essential', '本质的,基本的;净化的 (adj.)；本质;要素 (n.)', 'adj.', '/ɪ''senʃ(ə)l/', '{"meaning":"本质的,基本的;净化的 (adj.)；本质;要素 (n.)","examples":["The essential difference between Sam and me was the fact that I took life seriously. — 我和萨姆的根本区别在于我是认真对待生活的。","The essential point of relay racing is that it is a team effort. — 接力赛跑的基本要点是讲究团队配合。","essential oil — 香精油，精油"],"etymology":null}', 1005),
(3, 'presence', 'presence', '出席,到场,存在,在 (n.)', 'n.', '/''prez(ə)ns/', '{"meaning":"出席,到场,存在,在 (n.)","examples":["Your presence is requested at the club meeting on Friday. — 敬请出席于周五举行的俱乐部会议。","in the presence of — 在…面前；有某人在场","in presence of — 提示"],"etymology":null}', 1006),
(3, 'present', 'present', '出席的,现在的 (adj.)；现在,礼物 (n.)；赠送,提出 (v.)', 'adj.', '/''prez(ə)nt/', '{"meaning":"出席的,现在的 (adj.)；现在,礼物 (n.)；赠送,提出 (v.)","examples":["the present situation of the millions of people who are suffering poverty and disease — 遭受贫困和疾病折磨的数百万人民的现状","present oneself — 出席","at present — 目前，现在"],"etymology":null}', 1007),
(3, 'presently', 'presently', '一会儿,不久;现在,目前 (adv.)', 'adv.', '/''prez(ə)ntlɪ/', '{"meaning":"一会儿,不久;现在,目前 (adv.)","examples":["The doctor will be here presently. — 医生一会儿就到。","Presently, I fell asleep. — 一会儿我就睡着了。"],"etymology":null}', 1008),
(3, 'represent', 'represent', '描述,表示;代表,代理;阐明,说明 (v.)', 'v.', '/reprɪ''zent/', '{"meaning":"描述,表示;代表,代理;阐明,说明 (v.)","examples":["Mr Kobayashi was chosen to represent the company at the conference. — 小林先生被选中代表公司出席会议。","represent something to oneself — 想像出某事物","represent for — 代表；象征"],"etymology":null}', 1009),
